@Sabemi.PaymentWebhook.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5095

### Exemplo usando API Key
POST {{Sabemi.PaymentWebhook.Api_HostAddress}}/webhooks/pagamento
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-KEY: sabemi-dev-api-key

{
  "id_transacao": "TRX-20260610-0001",
  "id_contrato": "CTR-123456",
  "valor": 1500.75,
  "data_pagamento": "2026-06-10T21:43:02.178Z",
  "status": "PAGO"
}

### Exemplo usando Signature (HMAC-SHA256)
### Para calcular a signature:
### 1. Pega o payload JSON bruto (exatamente como é enviado na requisição)
### 2. Calcula HMAC-SHA256 usando o secret "sabemi-dev-signature-secret-123456"
### 3. Converte para hexadecimal em lowercase
### 
### Payload usado para cálculo (com formatação):
### {
###   "id_transacao": "TRX-20260610-0001",
###   "id_contrato": "CTR-123456",
###   "valor": 1500.75,
###   "data_pagamento": "2026-06-10T21:43:02.178Z",
###   "status": "PAGO"
### }
### Signature calculada: 0b1e0099db2325c261e9d9689545bd0c0d915e6ed569d28f97cdd8bdb8ee737e
POST {{Sabemi.PaymentWebhook.Api_HostAddress}}/webhooks/pagamento
Content-Type: application/json
X-Signature: 0b1e0099db2325c261e9d9689545bd0c0d915e6ed569d28f97cdd8bdb8ee737e

{
  "id_transacao": "TRX-20260610-0001",
  "id_contrato": "CTR-123456",
  "valor": 1500.75,
  "data_pagamento": "2026-06-10T21:43:02.178Z",
  "status": "PAGO"
}

